item.title: CVE-2023-45799|2023-10-30T06:17:21.370Z -- mlsoft -- tco%21stream
item.description: In MLSoft TCO!stream versions 8.0.22.1115 and below, a vulnerability exists due to insufficient permission validation. This allows an attacker to make the victim download and execute arbitrary files.
